        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://losangeles.craigslist.org/sgv/sec/6046296914.html"></div>
        </div>
Colony Guard Services are looking for an experienced unarmed security guard for a part time (36 hours/week) position. This position pays $11/hour.<br>
<br>
PRIMARY RESPONSIBILITIES:<br>
*Protect property and lives by patrolling the area.<br>
*Identify visitors and ask for appropriate documents if need be.<br>
*Stop possible suspicious activity and ask for identification.<br>
*Reach out to local police if a physical altercation occurs.<br>
*Keep a neat and professional appearance at all job sites.<br>
*Guard against theft and maintain security.<br>
*Respond to alarms and calls of distress.<br>
*Open doors for customers<br>
*Must be attentive and aware of your surroundings at all times<br>
*Provide OUTSTANDING customer service to all customers/employees at assigned post.<br>
<br>
QUALIFICATIONS<br>
*Active guard card<br>
*At least 1 year of security/military/ or public safety experience<br>
*Reliable transportation<br>
*Excellent communication skills (must be fluent in English)<br>
*Positive, honest, and loyal work ethic<br>
*Friendly and professional demeanor<br>
*Wiling to participate in our pre-employment process which includes a full background check<br>
*Bilingual in Spanish and English is a huge plus. <br>
*Flexible Schedule <br>
<br>
PHYSICAL REQUIREMENT<br>
Must be able to stand/walk for 7-8 hours a day.<br>
<br>
Salary: $11.00 /hour<br>
<br>
Required experience:<br>
<br>
Security/Military/or Public Safety: 1 year<br>
<br>
Please send your resume to colonyguardservices@gmail.com for consideration.    </section>

